`,(0,d.jsxDEV)(N,{name:"card-with-form",children:[(0,d.jsxDEV)(e.div,{"data-rehype-pretty-code-fragment":"",children:(0,d.jsxDEV)(e.pre,{"data-language":"tsx","data-theme":"default",__rawString__:`import * as React from "react"\r
\r
import { Button } from "@/components/ui/button"\r
import {\r
  Card,\r
  CardContent,\r
  CardDescription,\r
  CardFooter,\r
  CardHeader,\r
  CardTitle,\r
} from "@/components/ui/card"\r
import { Input } from "@/components/ui/input"\r
import { Label } from "@/components/ui/label"\r
import {\r
  Select,\r
  SelectContent,\r
  SelectItem,\r
  SelectTrigger,\r
  SelectValue,\r
} from "@/components/ui/select"\r
\r
export function CardWithForm() {\r
  return (\r
    <Card className="w-[350px]">\r
      <CardHeader>\r
        <CardTitle>Create project</CardTitle>\r
        <CardDescription>Deploy your new project in one-click.</CardDescription>\r
      </CardHeader>\r
      <CardContent>\r
        <form>\r
          <div className="grid w-full items-center gap-4">\r
            <div className="flex flex-col space-y-1.5">\r
              <Label htmlFor="name">Name</Label>\r
              <Input id="name" placeholder="Name of your project" />\r
            </div>\r
            <div className="flex flex-col space-y-1.5">\r
              <Label htmlFor="framework">Framework</Label>\r
              <Select>\r
                <SelectTrigger id="framework">\r
                  <SelectValue placeholder="Select" />\r
                </SelectTrigger>\r
                <SelectContent position="popper">\r
                  <SelectItem value="next">Next.js</SelectItem>\r
                  <SelectItem value="sveltekit">SvelteKit</SelectItem>\r
                  <SelectItem value="astro">Astro</SelectItem>\r
                  <SelectItem value="nuxt">Nuxt.js</SelectItem>\r
                </SelectContent>\r
              </Select>\r
            </div>\r
          </div>\r
        </form>\r
      </CardContent>\r
      <CardFooter className="flex justify-between">\r
        <Button variant="outline">Cancel</Button>\r
        <Button>Deploy</Button>\r
      </CardFooter>\r
    </Card>\r
  )\r
}\r

\r
import { Button } from "@/components/ui/button"\r
import {\r
  Card,\r
  CardContent,\r
  CardDescription,\r
  CardFooter,\r
  CardHeader,\r
  CardTitle,\r
} from "@/components/ui/card"\r
import { Input } from "@/components/ui/input"\r
import { Label } from "@/components/ui/label"\r
import {\r
  Select,\r
  SelectContent,\r
  SelectItem,\r
  SelectTrigger,\r
  SelectValue,\r
} from "@/components/ui/select"\r
\r
export function CardWithForm() {\r
  return (\r
    <Card className="w-[350px]">\r
      <CardHeader>\r
        <CardTitle>Create project</CardTitle>\r
        <CardDescription>Deploy your new project in one-click.</CardDescription>\r
      </CardHeader>\r
      <CardContent>\r
        <form>\r
          <div className="grid w-full items-center gap-4">\r
            <div className="flex flex-col space-y-1.5">\r
              <Label htmlFor="name">Name</Label>\r
              <Input id="name" placeholder="Name of your project" />\r
            </div>\r
            <div className="flex flex-col space-y-1.5">\r
              <Label htmlFor="framework">Framework</Label>\r
              <Select>\r
                <SelectTrigger id="framework">\r
                  <SelectValue placeholder="Select" />\r
                </SelectTrigger>\r
                <SelectContent position="popper">\r
                  <SelectItem value="next">Next.js</SelectItem>\r
                  <SelectItem value="sveltekit">SvelteKit</SelectItem>\r
                  <SelectItem value="astro">Astro</SelectItem>\r
                  <SelectItem value="nuxt">Nuxt.js</SelectItem>\r
                </SelectContent>\r
              </Select>\r
            </div>\r
          </div>\r
        </form>\r
      </CardContent>\r
      <CardFooter className="flex justify-between">\r
        <Button variant="outline">Cancel</Button>\r
        <Button>Deploy</Button>\r
      </CardFooter>\r
    </Card>\r
  )\r
}\r
